vise Champion of Champions |work=Champion of Champions Snooker |date=12 June 2013 |access-date=7 January 2020 |url=http://www.championofchampionssnooker.co.uk/itv4-to-televise-champion-of-champions/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522191645/http://www.championofchampionssnooker.co.uk/itv4-to-televise-champion-of-champions/ |archive-date=22 May 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"snoo_Cham\">{{Cite web |title=Champion of Champions (2019) |website=snooker.org |access-date=4 November 2019 |url=http://www.snooker.org/res/brackets.asp?event=850}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"cham_Priz\">{{Cite web |title=Prize Fund |work=Champion of Champions Snooker |access-date=4 November 2019 |url=http://www.championofchampionssnooker.co.uk/prize-fund/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107135409/http://www.championofchampionssnooker.co.uk/prize-fund/ |archive-date=7 January 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"2019qualification\">{{cite web |url=http://www.championofchampionssnooker.co.uk/players/ |title=Qualified Players |access-date=14 May 2019 |work=Champion of Champions Snooker |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107135501/http://www.championofchampionssnooker.co.uk/players/ |archive-date=7 January 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"wpbs_Cham\">{{Cite web |title=Champion of Champions 2019 \u2013 Crawley Update |work=WPBSA |access-date=12 February 2020 |url=https://www.wpbsa.com/champion-of-champions-2019-crawley-update/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191026010957/https://www.wpbsa.com/champion-of-champions-2019-crawley-update/ |archive-date=26 October 2019 |url-status=live |date=21 October 2019}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"seeds\">{{Cite web |title=ManBetX Champion of Champions draw made as world snooker stars head to Coventry |last=Rodger |first=James |website=[[Coventry Telegraph|CoventryLive]] |access-date=15 February 2020 |url=https://www.coventrytelegraph.net/news/coventry-news/manbetx-champion-champions-draw-made-17180437 |a