-nooh-to-reach-champion-of-champions-semis_sto7527376/story.shtml}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"O5izV\">{{Cite web |title=Champion of Champions: Ronnie O'Sullivan survives scare against Jimmy White before making semi-finals |work=Sporting Life |location=UK |date=7 November 2019 |access-date=18 November 2019 |url=https://www.sportinglife.com/snooker/news/osullivan-survives-whirlwind-scare/173778}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"semi2\">{{Cite news |title=Judd Trump beats Mark Allen in Champion of Champions semis |newspaper=[[BBC Sport]] |date=9 November 2019 |access-date=6 December 2019 |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/snooker/50363501}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"b20d9\">{{cite web |title=ManBetX Champion of Champions \u2013 Centuries |url=http://livescores.worldsnookerdata.com/Centuries/CenturyBreaks/14126/manbetx-champion-of-champions |website=World Snooker |date=4\u201310 November 2019}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"snooker.org\">{{Cite web |title=ManBetX Champion of Champions (2019) |trans-title= |website=snooker.org |access-date=9 December 2019 |url=http://www.snooker.org/res/index.asp?event=850}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"eurosport final\">{{Cite web |title=Emotional Robertson beats Trump in thrilling Champion of Champions final |first=James |last=Gray |work=Eurosport UK |date=10 November 2019 |access-date=9 December 2019 |url=https://www.eurosport.co.uk/snooker/champion-of-champions/2019-2020/snooker-news-neil-robertson-beats-judd-trump-in-thrilling-champion-of-champions-final_sto7533646/story.shtml}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"BBC final\">{{Cite news |title=Champion of Champions: Neil Robertson beats Judd Trump 10\u20139 in dramatic final |newspaper=[[BBC Sport]] |date=10 November 2019 |access-date=9 December 2019 |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/snooker/50368239 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111131203/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/snooker/50368239 |archive-date=11 November 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"snoo_188B\">{{Cite web |title=188BET Champion of Champions (2015) |trans-title= |website=snooker.org |access-date=9 December 2019 |url=http://www.snooker.org/res/index.asp?event=408 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150830012051/http://www.snooker.org/res/index.asp?event=408 |archive-date=30 August 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"snoo_Neil\">{{Cite web |title=Neil Robertson Wins Champion of Champions Title |author=Caulfield, David |work=SnookerHQ |date=11 November 2019 |access-date=9 December 2019 |url=https://snookerhq.com/2019/11/11/neil-robertson-wins-champion-of-champions-title/}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"vnrml\">{{cite web |url=https://wst.tv/tournaments/champion-of-champions-2019/ |title=ManbetX Champion of Champions |work=World Snooker |date=27 March 2019 |accessdate=7 February 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111141143/https://wst.tv/tournaments/champion-of-champions-2019/ |archive-date=11 January 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"lyYHz\">{{cite web |title=O'Sullivan earns Champion of Champions crown |url=http://www.espn.co.uk/snooker/sport/story/260457.html?CMP=OTC-RSS |publisher=ESPN |website=espn.co.uk |date=24 November 2013 |accessdate=24 November 2013 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6LV6G6c9D?url=http://www.espn.co.uk/snooker/sport/story/260457.html?CMP=OTC-RSS |archivedate=29 November 2013 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"CPmTD\">{{cite web |url=http://www.snooker.org/res/index.asp?template=2 |website=snooker.org |title=2019\u201320 snooker season |accessdate=7 February 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723205846/http://www.snooker.org/res/index.asp?template=2 |archive-date=23 July 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"s1AI7\">{{Cite web |title=World Seniors Championship Added To ManBetX Champion Of Champions Qualification Criteria |work=Champion of Champions Snooker |date=20 August 2019 |access-date=4 November 2019 |url=http://www.championofchampionssnooker.co.uk/world-seniors-championship-added-manbetx-champion-champions-qualification-criteria/ |archive-ur